# Manual HTTP calls for the consolidated listing — hit the RUNNING app (dev database).
# Pick the "dev" environment. GET /candidatures/consolidated returns { data[], meta{} }.
# Only candidatures WITH an evaluator appear. Each row carries the evaluator's total and
# the concatenated emails of that evaluator's candidates.

### Default listing (order: years_of_experience desc, page 1, 15 per page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated
Accept: application/json

### Order by evaluator name, ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?sort=evaluator_name&direction=asc
Accept: application/json

### Order by the per-evaluator total (an aggregate), descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?sort=evaluator_total&direction=desc
Accept: application/json

### Filter by candidate name prefix (index-friendly LIKE 'A%')
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?filter[full_name]=A
Accept: application/json

### Filter by exact years of experience
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?filter[years_of_experience]=9
Accept: application/json

### Pagination: 5 per page, page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?per_page=5&page=2
Accept: application/json

### Combined: filter + sort + pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?filter[evaluator_name]=M&sort=years_of_experience&direction=desc&per_page=5
Accept: application/json

### Invalid sort column (expect 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidatures/consolidated?sort=drop_table
Accept: application/json
